quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  41,45,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, nde luutondira e mayre. Si wanaano Konngol ardinoongol immorde ka Joomi maa, hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Гұaaweteno. KamЙ“e kan, pellet, hiЙ“e e sikke sikkitiiЙ—o nde"
  41,46,"Kala golluЙ—o ko moЖҙЖҙi, ko fii hoore-makko; kala kadi bonnuЙ—o, yantay e makko. Joomi maa siforaali wonnde, tooГұoowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  41,47,"Ko ka Makko woni ko ganndal Darngal ruttetee. DimЙ—e yaltataa e coomЙ—i mun, deyel (woo) saawataa,ngel jibintaa si wanaa e ganndal Makko.Г‘alnde O noddiroyta Й“e:\"Ko honto woni kafidaaЙ—i Am Й—in?\", Й“e wi'a:\"Men anndinii Ma, alah e amen seedotooЙ—o [Й—um]"
  41,48,ЖҒe majjira e kon ko Й“e rewaynoo ko adii; Й“e yananee wonnde daЙ—irgal alanaa Й“e
  41,49,"NeЙ—Й—anke on haaЙ“ataa toragol moЖҙЖҙere. Si bone memii mo, ko o taЖҙotooЙ—o, yonndiniiЙ—o"
  41,50,"Si Men meeЙ—inir mo moЖҙЖҙere immorde ka Amen, Й“aawo nde lorra memi mo, ko pellet o wi'ay: \"ЖҠum Й—oo ko min ! Mi fellitaani si Darngal daroto. Si mi ruttaama ka Joomi am, ko pellet, moЖҙЖҙere hino woodani lam ka Makko\". Ma Men humpitu yedduЙ“e Й“en, fii ko Й“e huuwi kon, ko ma Men meeЙ—inoy Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  41,51,"Si Men neeminii e neЙ—Й—anke on, o Й—uurnoo o toowna balaaje makko; si bone non heЙ“ii mo, o wona jom toraare yaajunde"
  41,52,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, si wonii le ko ka Allah nde iwri, refti yedduЙ—on nde; haray ko hommbo Й“uri majjude on wonЙ—o e lurral woЙ—Й—ungal"
  41,53,"Aray Men holla Й“e maandeeji Amen Й—in ka tatteeji e maЙ“Й“e tigi, haa Й“anngana Й“e wonnde ko nde goonga. E yonaali wonnde Joomi maa, ko O seediiЙ—o kala huunde"
  41,54,"Anndee hiЙ“e e sikke fii hawroygol e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Anndee non, ko O huЙ“indiiЙ—o kala huunde"